{"tid":387915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【隨機犯案】矽谷男入屋打劫兼雞姦男戶主 檢控官：任職40年首見","createTime":"2017-09-05T04:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T13:10:24.000Z","uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"072849618060e69357e5d43bd2546fb2957d8762","tid":387915,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>【隨機犯案】矽谷男入屋打劫兼雞姦男戶主 檢控官：任職40年首見</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504584332_c904.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504584332_c904.jpg&h=20708fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加州矽谷有一名男子於上月在門洛公園市（Menlo Park）隨機進入一間住宅打劫並性侵屋內的六旬男戶主。涉事的男劫匪日前出庭應訊，負責案件的檢控官表示在他任職40多年來，第一次見到一宗男子隨機入屋打劫後再雞姦男子的案件。<br />\n<br />\n36歲男疑犯史蒂文斯（Lamar Dekari Stevens）被指於8月11日清晨時分潛入一間住宅，並持刀威迫屋內男戶主就範。男戶主在交出40美元（約312港元）後被對方雞姦。男戶主其後成功逃脫並向鄰居求助。<br />\n<br />\n史蒂文斯於案發同日晚上為了躲避警方拘捕，爬過圍籬並從30英呎（約9米）高的地方跳下，令他腳腕扭傷，住院一周後才出院。<br />\n<br />\n他於上周二出庭應訊，他被訴強制肛交及入屋行劫等10項重罪。聖馬刁縣地區檢察官瓦格斯塔夫（Steve Wagstaffe）表示，這是他40年來第一次見到到這種男子隨機入屋打劫後再性侵男子的案件。史蒂文斯一旦罪成，最高可被判終身監禁並最少須服刑25年。"},{"pid":"03d74adc713aefd3c562630231f78ee70a6acf9a","tid":387915,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"Nigga又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294d4e809b5ee69cc03418ee757a1907562c002e","tid":387915,"uid":7140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"Nigga gank"},{"pid":"5de486955a00c980dde019c252dbf8df16c2b0df","tid":387915,"uid":17081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"六十路男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6eef8163a5aa36d209bac205ed493b81e124ff4","tid":387915,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"點解會有人煲老藕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1398bbfd2dac3023fee8b32c029665260739b2f","tid":387915,"uid":126293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2015-09/16/4/campaign_images/webdr14/britain-is-to-have-its-first-gay-old-peoples-home-2-7428-1442390515-3_dblbig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.buzzfeed.com%2Fbuzzfeed-static%2Fstatic%2F2015-09%2F16%2F4%2Fcampaign_images%2Fwebdr14%2Fbritain-is-to-have-its-first-gay-old-peoples-home-2-7428-1442390515-3_dblbig.jpg&h=de413a50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e32c246cc39c15ac727cb6349bffe3c65ae38c4","tid":387915,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"黑人至上主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4881c74d0eefffc76de13c1041c5e2072c55ab8","tid":387915,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:10:24.000Z","msg":"40蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}